1
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:10,360
It's you.

2
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:13,400
You've grown so much.

3
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:17,940
Why are you back in Malaya?

4
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:19,080
Uncle Lin.

5
00:01:19,360 --> 00:01:20,960
I came this time because Brother Mingshu

6
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:21,920
sent me a letter

7
00:01:22,080 --> 00:01:23,480
saying he had news of my parents

8
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:25,039
and asking me to come to Malaya immediately.

9
00:01:25,039 --> 00:01:26,200
I didn't expect to meet Wangshu

10
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:27,120
on the boat here,

11
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:28,520
so we came here together.

12
00:01:30,039 --> 00:01:30,480
Dad.

13
00:01:31,240 --> 00:01:32,500
Any news of my brother?

14
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:34,200
Not yet.

15
00:01:35,440 --> 00:01:35,840
These past few days,

16
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:37,300
we've been looking for him

17
00:01:37,520 --> 00:01:38,440
but haven't been able to

18
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:39,700
find his whereabouts.

19
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:41,240
It's been almost a month.

20
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:42,920
I think Brother Mingshu

21
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,360
must have found out something

22
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:45,490
and ran into danger.

23
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:47,729
We need to find him as soon as possible.

24
00:01:48,320 --> 00:01:48,720
Right.

25
00:01:49,039 --> 00:01:50,680
The old newspapers in my brother's room.

26
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:52,680
Come, let's go. I'll take you there.

27
00:01:59,960 --> 00:02:01,160
Found it. Right here.

28
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:04,120
Wanted Poster.

29
00:02:05,360 --> 00:02:06,880
A Chinese couple,

30
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:09,500
dissatisfied with the tea factory's wages,

31
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:11,120
incited workers to protest,

32
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:13,200
murdered the Japanese president,

33
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:14,920
and stole an important list.

34
00:02:15,720 --> 00:02:18,120
They also set fire to the Japanese tea factory.

35
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,600
Since the crime, the couple

36
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:20,680
has been missing.

37
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:24,120
A city-wide manhunt is now issued for them.

38
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:26,160
Anyone with information

39
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:27,440
should report immediately.

40
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:29,600
June 8, 1928.

41
00:02:31,320 --> 00:02:31,880
Jiadong.

42
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:34,079
I remember my brother mentioning

43
00:02:34,079 --> 00:02:34,760
that the day you were sent here

44
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:35,690
twelve years ago

45
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:36,960
was in June

46
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:38,800
1928.

47
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:39,880
Right.

48
00:02:40,040 --> 00:02:41,160
It's in the remittance records.

49
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:42,820
The sending date was June 7th.

50
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:45,200
Mingshu wrote in the remittance

51
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:46,960
that he has my parents' whereabouts.

52
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,560
Could it be related to

53
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,090
this Japanese tea factory?

54
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:51,520
Could the wanted couple on this

55
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,120
be...?

56
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:52,920
That's right.

57
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,200
The ones they are after

58
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:56,360
are your parents.

59
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:57,770
Did you hear?

60
00:02:58,320 --> 00:02:59,000
Last night,

61
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,560
something terrible happened at the tea factory.

62
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,890
Dozens of Chinese died,

63
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,900
including over ten children.

64
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:06,160
It's one thing for these damn Japanese

65
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:07,040
to bully us Chinese

66
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,200
on a daily basis.

67
00:03:08,880 --> 00:03:11,340
But now they dare to commit arson and murder.

68
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:13,180
They are absolutely lawless.

69
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:15,140
A family of three escaped.

70
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:15,800
Now the Japanese

71
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,400
are searching the whole city.

72
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,880
Look at how big the fire is.

73
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:23,520
It seems this tea factory

74
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,600
definitely has a problem.

75
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:25,720
The Japanese are twisting the truth

76
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:26,520
to cover it up.

77
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:27,800
They're just using the tea factory

78
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:28,440
as a cover.

79
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,360
To hide

80
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,920
the crimes they've committed.

81
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:32,180
Do you know something?

82
00:03:33,640 --> 00:03:34,640
When I came here, I saw

83
00:03:34,640 --> 00:03:36,000
a letter written by my dad.

84
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,280
It recorded in detail

85
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,600
that they've been secretly using Chinese

86
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:40,200
for human experimentation.

87
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:41,880
Human experimentation?

88
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:42,410
Exactly.

89
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:44,000
Those animals.

90
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:45,800
I think my brother must have

91
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,000
found out something.

92
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,160
That's why he went to the northern suburbs to collect the letters.

93
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:50,090
What do you mean?

94
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:53,090
The Japanese tea factory is in the northern suburbs.

95
00:03:53,480 --> 00:03:54,079
Uncle Lin.

96
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,760
I'll go to the tea factory tonight

97
00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:56,420
to find out.

98
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:56,880
No.

99
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:59,490
It's too dangerous to go like this.

100
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,850
We need a thorough plan.

101
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:02,920
If Brother Mingshu is really at the tea factory,

102
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:05,120
wouldn't we miss the chance to save him?

103
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,980
This is no trivial matter.

104
00:04:08,200 --> 00:04:10,280
Let me ask around privately first.

105
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:11,320
As for you,

106
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:13,060
find a place to stay first.

107
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:14,220
When there is news,

108
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,240
I will notify you.

109
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,120
Dad.

110
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:17,480
Let Brother Jiadong

111
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:18,240
stay here.

112
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:20,200
He can help us investigate

113
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:21,720
my brother's whereabouts.

114
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,480
Besides,

115
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:23,840
aren't we just short of a

116
00:04:23,840 --> 00:04:24,720
letter writer?

117
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:26,660
No, he can't stay here.

118
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:29,240
If your brother's disappearance

119
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,700
is related to this matter,

120
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:32,040
then our Wansheng Remittance Agency

121
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,640
would have been targeted long ago.

122
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:35,770
It would be unsafe for him to stay here.

123
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:37,530
Jiadong,

124
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:38,880
I will

125
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,480
write you a

126
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,520
recommendation letter now.

127
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:43,080
I'll recommend you to the Zhicheng Remittance Agency.

128
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:43,560
Over there...

129
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,480
I was just short of a courier.

130
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:44,960
No.

131
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:47,159
I'm keeping Jiadong here today.

132
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:48,640
No one can stop me.

133
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:50,720
Not even the King of Heaven himself.

134
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:51,650
Wangshu, you...

135
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,320
What's all the noise?

136
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:02,410
Why so angry?

137
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:04,200
Inspector Luo is here.

138
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,480
Luo Wang, why are you here again?

139
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:08,570
I've figured it out.

140
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,640
I've thought it through.

141
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:12,480
I am your

142
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:13,360
Mr. Right.

143
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,690
I came here this time

144
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:19,800
to propose to you.

145
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:23,240
I've told you many times.

146
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,500
I will never marry you.

147
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,060
I'm unmarried,

148
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,160
and so are you.

149
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:30,770
Don't deprive me

150
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:32,280
of my right to pursue you.

151
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:37,690
Who said I'm unmarried?

152
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,240
Come here.

153
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:41,640
This

154
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,760
is the man my father arranged for me

155
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:44,840
in Quanzhou when we were babies.

156
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:45,900
He is my fiancé now.

157
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,280
He came to Malaya this time...

158
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:48,320
He came here to marry me.

159
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:50,180
Ask my dad if you don't believe me.

160
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:54,970
Father-in-law.

161
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,220
Inspector Luo.

162
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,940
I forgot to introduce him.

163
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:58,520
This

164
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,920
is my daughter's fiancé.

165
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:03,640
He came here specifically for the wedding.

166
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:10,650
Hello, Officer Luo.

167
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:12,200
I am Wangshu's fiancé.

168
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,690
My name is Chen Jiadong.

169
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:20,640
Who are you?

170
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,260
Do you know who I am?

171
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:25,690
Get lost.

172
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:33,360
Wangshu.

173
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,380
You can make excuses to me,

174
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:36,000
but you don't have to use

175
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,200
a pretty boy like him.

176
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:39,360
It's bad for your reputation,

177
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:39,760
right?

178
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:41,040
Besides, I don't buy it anyway.

179
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,280
Believe it or not.

180
00:06:42,280 --> 00:06:43,520
He is my fiancé now.

181
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:53,840
Wangshu.

182
00:06:53,840 --> 00:06:54,440
Come here.

183
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:55,760
Stand over here a bit.

184
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:56,840
Come, stand here.

185
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:58,960
Who are you?

186
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,360
Do you want to die?

187
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:02,000
I...

188
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:04,260
Don't touch my fiancé.

189
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:07,050
Wangshu.

190
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,540
Move out of the way.

191
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:22,280
I'm not playing anymore.

192
00:07:23,080 --> 00:07:24,480
We still have a long time.

193
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,610
We've got a feud now.

194
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,200
Just you wait.

195
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:40,450
Sheriff.

196
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:41,490
What date is set,

197
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:42,040
and how many tables are booked for the banquet?

198
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:42,680
Set my ass.

199
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:47,600
From now on,

200
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:50,040
keep an eye on Wansheng Trading Company.

201
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:52,370
There's a man named Chen Jiadong in there.

202
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,600
Who did I ask you to keep an eye on?

203
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,740
Chen... Chen Jiadong.

204
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,680
How improper is this.

205
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:07,400
As a girl,

206
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,080
in public,

207
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:10,360
kissing a strange man?

208
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:11,880
If word gets out,

209
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:13,280
how will you get married?

210
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:15,120
I want to.

211
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:18,400
Dad.

212
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:19,400
You can't drive

213
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:20,560
Jiadong away now, can you?

214
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,320
After all,

215
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:22,320
you admitted in front of Luo Wang

216
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:23,840
that he is your son-in-law.

217
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:24,200
You!

218
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:27,480
You really piss me off.

219
00:08:29,400 --> 00:08:30,200
Fine.

220
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:32,559
Then you can stay.

221
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,020
Here, give it to me.

222
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:47,000
Thank you.

223
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:00,810
That man just now was...

224
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,240
Luo Wang.

225
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,920
He's the police chief.

226
00:09:05,560 --> 00:09:06,840
He has always...

227
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:09,960
You don't need to worry about it.

228
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:13,690
Thank you, Wangshu.

229
00:09:13,920 --> 00:09:14,720
I'm sure we will

230
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:16,080
find Mingshu.

231
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:18,320
Why don't we go

232
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,640
to the tea factory tonight to look around.

233
00:09:19,640 --> 00:09:21,160
No, it's too dangerous.

234
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:22,680
But what if my brother

235
00:09:22,680 --> 00:09:24,280
is really at the tea factory?

236
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,280
If we find him,

237
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:25,840
won't we know

238
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,170
where your parents are?

239
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:29,360
Okay.

240
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:31,520
Then I'll go to the northern suburbs tomorrow to collect the batch.

241
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:33,680
I'll also ask around privately while I'm there.

242
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:34,800
Then I'll go with you.

243
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:35,200
No.

244
00:09:35,560 --> 00:09:36,890
What if it's dangerous?

245
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:38,000
I'll go by myself.

246
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:39,650
Don't worry.

247
00:09:39,880 --> 00:09:40,800
Even if there's news,

248
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:42,000
I won't act rashly.

249
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,520
Then you must be careful.

250
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:52,720
I will.
